flowchart TD
    C([Consumer]) --> SHOP["/shop — Product discovery grid"]

    SHOP --> STORES["Store carousel (horizontally scrollable)"]
    STORES -->|click store| STORE_PAGE["/shop/store_[id]"]

    SHOP --> GRID["Product grid\n2 cols mobile / 4-5 cols desktop"]
    STORE_PAGE --> FILTERED["Filtered product grid\nfor single retailer"]

    GRID -->|click product| MODAL["ProductDetailModal\nimage · price · stock · HSN · specs"]
    FILTERED -->|click product| MODAL

    MODAL --> ADD_BTN["Add to Cart button"]
    GRID -->|click Add to Cart| ADD_BTN

    ADD_BTN --> AUTH_CHECK{Logged in?}
    AUTH_CHECK -->|No| LOGIN["/login?redirect=/shop\nWhatsApp OTP"]
    LOGIN -->|success| ADD_BTN

    AUTH_CHECK -->|Yes| CART_API["POST /api/cart\nUpsert cart_item\nOne cart per retailer"]

    CART_API --> BADGE["Cart badge updates\nitemCount in header"]

    BADGE -->|open drawer| DRAWER["CartDrawer\nItems grouped by store\nQuantity controls\nSubtotal + GST breakdown"]

    DRAWER --> CHECKOUT["Checkout button\n(payment flow pending)"]
